The Diamond Sutra has inspired Jack Kerouac and the Dalai Lama. Its journey has coincided with the growing appeal of Buddhism in the West. As the Gutenberg Age cedes to the Google Age, the survival of the Silk RoadÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s greatest treasure is testament to the endurance of the written word.
